\li{\strong{Functional Testing}}
\li{Verify application integrations}
\li{Monitor logs for errors}
\li{\strong{Image Verification}}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{Phase 5: Documentation and Cleanup}
\ol{
\li{\strong{Update Documentation}}
\li{Record migration completion dates}
\li{Update deployment documentation}
\li{Note configuration changes}
\li{\strong{Monitor Post-Migration}}
\li{Monitor for 24–48 hours}
\li{Check for performance issues}
\li{Validate image pulls}
}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{5. Common Issues and Solutions}
\ul{
\li{\startverb **Issue 1: StatefulSet Update Restrictions**\\stopverb}
}

\ul{
\li{\startverb **Issue 2: Image Pull Errors**\\stopverb}
}

\ul{
\li{\startverb **Issue 3: Configuration Drift**\\stopverb}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{6. Security Considerations}
\ul{
\li{\code{\startverb allowInsecureImages\stopverb} is required for Bitnami Legacy but should be monitored.}
\li{Implement image vulnerability scanning.}
\li{Plan for migration away from Legacy images long-term.}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{7. Rollback Procedures}
\ul{
\li{\strong{Immediate Rollback:} Revert Terraform configuration to the previous version.}
\li{\strong{Helm Rollback:}}
\li{\strong{Emergency:} Switch back to \code{\startverb bitnami\stopverb} repository (if still available).}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{8. Timeline Recommendations}
\ul{
\li{\strong{Pre-August 28th, 2025:} Complete staging and sandbox migrations.}
\li{\strong{August 28th, 2025:} Execute production migration.}
\li{\strong{Post-Migration:} Monitor for one week, then plan a long-term strategy.}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{9. Long-term Strategy}
\p{Since the \strong{Bitnami Legacy repository is temporary}, consider:}

\ul{
\li{Bitnami Secure Images for supported production workloads.}
\li{Alternative chart providers.}
\li{Building and maintaining your own container images.}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{10. Migration Checklist}
\subtree{
\title{Pre-Migration}
\ul{
\li{[ ] Inventory all Bitnami deployments}
\li{[ ] Document current versions and configurations}
\li{[ ] Test migration process in staging}
\li{[ ] Prepare rollback procedures}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{Migration Execution}
\ul{
\li{[ ] Update Terraform configurations}
\li{[ ] Apply changes to staging environment}
\li{[ ] Validate staging deployment}
\li{[ ] Apply to sandbox, validate deployment}
\li{[ ] Apply to production, validate deployment}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{Post-Migration}
\ul{
\li{[ ] Verify all services are functional}
\li{[ ] Monitor for 24–48 hours}
\li{[ ] Update documentation}
\li{[ ] Define long-term strategy}
}
}
}
}